  07 Dec 2006; Nguyễn Thái Ngọc Duy <pclouds@gentoo.org>
  gorua-0.17.ebuild:
  Remove ruby-zlib dependency. Require at least ruby-1.8 as ruby-zlib has
  been included since then. Bug #131978

*gorua-0.17 (08 Sep 2004)

  08 Sep 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +files/bookmarks_sample, +files/goRua.sh,
  +files/gorua-bbsmenu-update-gentoo.diff, +gorua-0.17.ebuild:
  Moved net-www/gorua to www-client/gorua.

  16 May 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> gorua-0.16-r2.ebuild,
  gorua-0.17.ebuild, files/bookmarks_sample,
  files/gorua-0.16-ruby18-gentoo.diff:
  Updated bookmarks_sample. Marked 0.17 stable on x86 and alpha.
  Removed old ebuild.

  27 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> gorua-0.16-r2.ebuild,
  gorua-0.17.ebuild:
  Add inherit eutils

*gorua-0.17 (12 Apr 2004)

  12 Apr 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> gorua-0.16-r2.ebuild,
  gorua-0.17.ebuild:
  Version bumped. virtual/ruby fix

  26 Dec 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> gorua-0.16-r1.ebuild:
  Changed sparc keyword to ~sparc as ruby-gtk has been masked until a few hours
  ago and hasn't had a chance to be properly tested.

*gorua-0.16-r2 (27 Dec 2003)

  27 Dec 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> gorua-0.16-r1.ebuild,
  gorua-0.16-r2.ebuild, gorua-0.16.ebuild,
  files/gorua-0.16-ruby18-gentoo.diff:
  Fixed runtime error on ruby 1.8. Forced ruby 1.6 for gorua-0.16-r1
  and marked as stable.

*gorua-0.16-r1 (13 Oct 2003)

